race.comment: TOMMY THUG (2) couldn't have been more impressive when saluting by eight lengths at Doomben last time out and will be high on confidence following that breakthrough victory. Thompson stays in the stirrups and is sure to be right there at the business end. EASY LOVE (1) is an honest commodity who has hit the top-five in all six starts to date. Strips fitter third-up and has to be included in calculations. THROTTLE RESPONSE (3) has gotten better with each run this campaign and looks to be working up to another win. Top-three contender. ORMOND ROAD (6) is usually thereabouts and looks one for the multiples. LET'S DO IT AGAIN (5) next best with the claim.
